<template>
    <vUpload :options="options"></vUpload>
</template>

<script>
import vUpload from '@c/dynamicSearch/upload/upload.vue'
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            options: {
                type: 'v_upload',
                key: 'uploadFile',
                uploadNum: 3,// 文件数量,默认为1，多张图片以，号拼接字符串形式提交
                fileSizeLimit: 3,// 文件大小  以兆为单位
            }
        }
    },
    components: {vUpload}
}
</script>
